headline: Morgan Stanley starts Parker-Hannifin at Equal-weight rating
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley initiated coverage of Parker-Hannifin Corp (NYSE:PH) with an Equal-weight rating and a $700 price target, saying the industrial firm’s transformation is already priced in after a 30% re-rating over the past two years.
